        schemaStream - - stream on XSD schema against which to validate. No validation is done if stream is NULL

      • getAdresseesFromContainer

        public static java.util.List<CapsuleAdressee> getAdresseesFromContainer(java.lang.Object containerObject)
                                                                 throws DhxException
        Method to fing adresssees from container. Method must return adressees for every existing version of the container, bacause service which uses that method does not know anything about container and just need adressees defined in it.
        Parameters:
        containerObject - - container(capsule) object from which to find adressees
        Returns:
        - list of the adresssees
        Throws:
        DhxException - - thrown adressees parsing is not defined for given object (capsule version)
